# ── DST world backup schedule ─────────────────────────
# Format: minute hour day month weekday command
#
# Run every hour at :05 past. The 5-minute offset avoids
# racing against DST's autosave (day transitions).
#
# To customise: edit this file, rebuild the image, and restart.
#   docker compose build dst-backup && docker compose up -d
#
5 * * * * /usr/local/bin/backup.sh
